-- MOVES- Advent International, RCS Capital and Old Mutual
-- 
-- Tue Sep 23, 2014 08:45AM EDT
-- None



Sept 23 (Reuters) - The following financial services industry appointments were announced on Tuesday. To inform us of other job changes, email moves@thomsonreuters.com.

ADVENT INTERNATIONAL CORP Private equity firm Advent International Corp said it had appointed Procter & Gamble Co <PG.N> executive Werner Geissler as an operating partner, effective from Jan. 1. [ID:nL3N0RO2ZH]  RCS CAPITAL CORP <RCAP.N> The investment firm said it appointed President Michael Weil as its chief executive, effective immediately. [ID:nL3N0RO3AN]  OLD MUTUAL GLOBAL INVESTORS The investment firm said that fund manager Ashton Bradbury would retire at the end of the year. [ID:nL6N0RO35Q]  RMB MORGAN STANLEY LTD